gurmukhi: kirnI Sbid su muK qy Awid bKwnIAY ]S`qRu Sbd ko AMq qvn ky TwnIAY ]skl qupk ky nwm su kib lih lIjIAY ]ho dIXo cho ijh Tvr qhwN hI dIjIAY ]1077]

gurmukhi: mdXDrnnI muK qy Awid BnIjIAY ]hMqw qwky AMq Sbd ko dIjIAY ]skl qupk ky nwm cqur icq mY lho ]ho khXo cho ien jhwN qhwN ien ko kho ]1078]

gurmukhi: isMDrnI muK Sbdwid bKwnIAY ]S`qRu Sbd ko AMq qvn kY TwnIAY ]skl qupk ky nwm su kib jIA jwnIAY ]ho Xw ky BIqr Byd nYk nhI mwnIAY ]1079]

gurmukhi: AinkpnI pd muK qy piRQm BxIjIAY ]S`qRu Sbd ko AMq qvn ky dIjIAY ]skl qupk ky nwm cqur jIA jwnIAY ]ho dXo cho ijh TvrY qhI pRmwnIAY ]1080]

gurmukhi: piRQm nwgnI muK qy Sbd aucwrIAY ]S`qRu Sbd khu AMq qvn ky fwrIAY ]skl qupk ky nwm suGr lih lIjIAY ]ho Xwky BIqr Byd nYk nhI kIjIAY ]1081]

gurmukhi: hrnI Sbd su muK qy Awid bKwnIAY ]S`qRu Sbd ko qwky AMq pRmwnIAY ]sB sRI nwm qupk ky cqur pCwnIAau ]ho jvnY Tvr su chIAY qhI bKwnIAau ]1082]

gurmukhi: gjnI Sbd bkqR qy Awid BxIjIAY ]S`qRu Sbd ko AMq qvn ky dIjIAY ]cqur qupk ky nwm skl lih lIjIAY ]ho ijh cwho iqh Tvr aucwrn kIjIAY ]
transliteration: Gadnishabad Baktra Te Aadh Bakhaaneeai|| Shattru Shabad Ko Ant Tavan Ke Deejeeai|| Ho Jih Chaaho Tih Thavar Ouchaaran Keejeeai||1083||

gurmukhi: swvjnI Sbdwid bKwnhu ]Ar pd AMq qvn ky Twnhu ]sB sRI nwm qupk ky lhIAY ]ijh TwN chy qNhI qy khIAY ]1084]

gurmukhi: mwqMgnI pdwir Bix`jY ]Ar pd AMq qvn ky id`jY ]sB sRI nwm qupk ky hovY ]jwco skl su kib iml jovY ]1085]
